description: This is a simple quiz game. Alexa will ask 10 questions and you have answer each question by number of correct answer. If you give wrong answer then Alexa will teach you correct answer. After answering all questions you will get the total score.
name: world largest smallest
shortDescription: A simple quiz game about world's largest and smallest things. Alexa will ask you 10 multiple questions with 4 options for each question.
